video.title: Fleabag Monkeyface
video.synopsis: Half-monkey half-boy Fleabag Monkeyface dives into gross adventures with his pals as they fend off the dastardly machinations of Dr. Dirk Spamflex.

episodes.synopsis: "Gross Out TV" investigates a fish-canning factory that's rumored to be haunted. / Gerald, Gene and Fleabag are VIP guests at World Vegetable Day.
